data.description: This home's floor plan was featured in Better Homes and Gardens.  Rare Thurston hills single level home featuring three bedrooms and two full baths on a huge nearly 1/4 acre lot.  Perfect for entertaining the home is built around the gorgeous "chalet" style custom covered deck with gorgeous exposed beams creating a wonderful backyard oasis.  The kitchen is light and bright with abundant cabinetry, laminate floors and direct access to the covered deck for entertaining. Living room features high vaulted ceilings, laminate floors and opens to the covered outdoor entertainment/living area.  Primary bedroom suite has direct access to the back deck oasis, large walk-in closet, soaking tub and walk-in shower.  This is an exceptional neighborhood embracing nature and featuring incredible views.  Parks and schools nearby.
